{
  "stem": "17374.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we go, like, from here to the city, that was already very, very far, that we, we took with us sandwiches and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a [INAUDIBLE], but it wasn't really far.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] maybe in an hour or even less than this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Cracow [INAUDIBLE] everything was smaller than it's here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything here is big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was a-- that was a [? house ?] which was really like a-- and I don't know how you call that, not a country.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Less than a country, that poor peasant, peasant house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't have roof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was straw, and not a floor, just clay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we have our quilt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] quilt, [INAUDIBLE] that was a big, [INAUDIBLE], and big pillows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father didn't work, and it was like a holiday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- remind me of the holiday when I was very little, [INAUDIBLE] and we have many people around us, all [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Poles ?] around us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And music was there, and dancing, because nobody was working.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, before?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, she did, at her shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when it was all this, all this come to stop, and we have to leave everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before, before the war it was like a grocery shop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It got everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near the [? main-- ?] where we live-- yes, it was in corner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was [POLISH]-- no, when I was born, it was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [POLISH] was the other street, and it was corner of [POLISH] and [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't have any name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think just a surname on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], a surname, I think-- that wasn't any name of that shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, in that place, in the first beginning, I was very young.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't work it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that is, that is-- Tonie is after the-- that, the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
